				<p>Source Lists power view management within Rebar and are the basis of Sidebars, Item Lists, Tab Bars, and Segmented Controls. Source Lists will always contain a list of buttons that when clicked change the contents of a target container found in <code>data-target</code> with the contents based on the <code>data-value</code> value. HTML examples for controls powered by Source Lists can be found in their own sections.</p>
